li-toolkit/spec.md\n/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/code-execution/design.md\n/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/code-execution/spec.md\n/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/project.md","metadata":{"count":99,"truncated":false},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z","time":{"start":1775849544812,"end":1775849544831}}}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775849544836,"sessionID":"ses_2871ec0bbffeG75S7Y1zWrjj42","part":{"id":"prt_d78e19c49001I9uekoWhT9OGn4","messageID":"msg_d78e1829d0016oJ714Zi6DEZ40","sessionID":"ses_2871ec0bbffeG75S7Y1zWrjj42","type":"tool","tool":"grep","callID":"toolu_tool-3be6b430d70e4cbbbf06d87a4b32704b","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"include":"*.md","pattern":"AR-009|Router.*HTTP|反向代理"},"output":"Found 19 matches\n/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/changes/AR-009/tasks.md:\n  Line 1: # AR-009 — Router HTTP 反向代理核心 Implementation Tasks\n\n/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/changes/AR-009/design.md:\n  Line 1: # AR-009 Design - Router HTTP Reverse Proxy Core\n  Line 5: The Router module provides HTTP reverse proxy capabilities for routing client requests to sandbox instances (AgentRuntime and CodeInterpreter). It acts as the entry point for all external traffic, managing session-based routing, authentication, and request forwarding.\n\n/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/.sdd_prompt.md:\n  Line 3: AR: AR-009 — Router HTTP 反向代理核心\n\n/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/changes/AR-009/delta-spec.md:\n  Line 1: # AR-009 Delta-Spec\n\n/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/proposal.md:\n  Line 1943: # AR-009 — Router HTTP 反向代理核心\n  Line 1947: 实现一个高性能 HTTP 反向代理核心，作为 AgentCube 运行时的入口点，负责将传入的 agent 请求路由到合适的后端服务。该模块将动态发现后端服务，提供负载均衡、健康检查、认证授权、可观测性等功能。\n  Line 1951: 为 AgentCube 平台提供 Router HTTP 反向代理核心，实现以下功能：\n  Line 2006: - gRPC 反向代理（推迟到未来迭代）\n  Line 2183: ### Alternative 3：gRPC 反向代理\n  Line 2185: **方法**：使用 gRPC 反向代理进行 agent 通信。\n\n/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/changes/AR-009/IMPLEMENTATION_SUMMARY.md:\n  Line 1: # AR-009 Implementation Summary\n\n/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/changes/AR-009/proposal.md:\n  Line 1: # AR-009 Proposal\n\n/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/changes/AR-009/spec.md:\n  Line 1: # AR-009 Spec\n\n/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/changes/AR-009/README.md:\n  Line 1: # AR-009 Implementation Notes\n\n/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/changes/AR-009/CHANGE.md:\n  Line 1: # AR-009 — Router HTTP 反向代理核心\n  Line 4: - **AR**: AR-009\n  Line 5: - **Title**: Router HTTP 反向代理核心\n\n/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/pkg/workloadmanager/design.md:\n  Line 1420: The Router calls the WorkloadManager HTTP API:","metadata":{"matches":19,"truncated":false},"title":"AR-009|Router.*HTTP|反向代理","time":{"start":1775849544818,"end":1775849544834}}}}
