{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775849555131,"sessionID":"ses_2871ec0bbffeG75S7Y1zWrjj42","part":{"id":"prt_d78e1c26d0017Drcfe6KAflV3U","messageID":"msg_d78e1b3ed001KH6bPdZjiEzwS5","sessionID":"ses_2871ec0bbffeG75S7Y1zWrjj42","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"toolu_tool-9c41fdad3d31405a84c3a1cbcb7926f0","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/changes/AR-009/IMPLEMENTATION_SUMMARY.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/changes/AR-009/IMPLEMENTATION_SUMMARY.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AR-009 Implementation Summary\n2: \n3: [To be filled]\n\n(End of file - total 3 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-009 Implementation Summary\n\n[To be filled]","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/changes/AR-009/IMPLEMENTATION_SUMMARY.md","time":{"start":1775849555113,"end":1775849555130}}}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775849555134,"sessionID":"ses_2871ec0bbffeG75S7Y1zWrjj42","part":{"id":"prt_d78e1c48f001OWCxcpC2gdjVcV","messageID":"msg_d78e1b3ed001KH6bPdZjiEzwS5","sessionID":"ses_2871ec0bbffeG75S7Y1zWrjj42","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"toolu_tool-a1bd406513d54a0ea8d61b117678f72f","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/changes/AR-009/tasks.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/changes/AR-009/tasks.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AR-009 — Router HTTP 反向代理核心 Implementation Tasks\n2: \n3: **Module**: `pkg/router`\n4: **Language**: Go\n5: **Size**: M\n6: **Design Stage**: ST-3 Completed\n7: \n8: ## Task Breakdown\n9: \n10: ### Task 1: Create package directory structure and documentation\n11: - [ ] Create `pkg/router` package directory\n12: - [ ] Create `doc.go` with package documentation\n13: - [ ] Create `README.md` with package overview\n14: - [ ] Add Go module imports for dependencies\n15:   - [ ] `github.com/gin-gonic/gin`\n16:   - [ ] `github.com/golang-jwt/jwt/v5`\n17:   - [ ] `golang.org/x/net/http2`\n18:   - [ ] `k8s.io/client-go`\n19:   - [ ] `k8s.io/klog/v2`\n20:   - [ ] Internal dependencies (`pkg/store`, `pkg/common/types`, `pkg/api`)\n21: - [ ] Verify package structure compiles\n22: \n23: **Verification**: Run `go build ./pkg/router` to ensure package structure is valid\n24: \n25: ---\n26: \n27: ### Task 2: Implement configuration structure\n28: - [ ] Create `pkg/router/config.go`\n29: - [ ] Define `Config` struct with fields:\n30:   - [ ] `Port string` - Server port (default: \"8080\")\n31:   - [ ] `Debug bool` - Debug mode flag\n32:   - [ ] `EnableTLS bool` - TLS enablement flag\n33:   - [ ] `TLSCert string` - TLS certificate path\n34:   - [ ] `TLSKey string` - TLS key path\n35:   - [ ] `MaxConcurrentRequests int` - Concurrency limit (